{"tid":1966143,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"荃錦公路保時捷撞山　車輪飛脫司機腰痛","createTime":"2020-04-10T03:41:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-10T03:49:40.000Z","uid":3090,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ed7d4f2f90a80b6036665b0a1e666b61ac4220ec","tid":1966143,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T03:41:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OE3ENWG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOE3ENWG.jpg&h=93815466&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今日(10日)凌晨零時許，一輛黃色保時捷Cayman私家車，沿荃錦公路落斜往荃灣方向行駛，當駛至川龍西煤氣檢管站一個左彎時，突然失控撞上山坡，車廂內安全氣袋彈出，車頭及車身損毀，右前輪亦飛脫，男司機一度被困車內，途經駕駛人士見狀，慌忙協助報警。<br />\n<br />\n救護員接報趕至，姓葉(43歲)司機報稱腰痛不適，需由救護車送院治理，警方正調查意外原因。據了解男司機疑因避狗肇禍。受事故影響，意外現場交通一度受阻。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UTomgQd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUTomgQd.jpg&h=fc1080f4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R0V7WQd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR0V7WQd.jpg&h=2cf591f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200410/mobile/bkn-20200410003845031-0410_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200410%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20200410003845031-0410_00822_001.html&d=GkP5J4C4AUyWsqXHyTPi62t2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=acf5cbf2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200410/mobile/bkn-20200410003845031-0410_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"03975e3b40bd0db18d0f06d63fa6991d353a062c","tid":1966143,"uid":353974,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T03:49:40.000Z","msg":"一睇就知飛車又控制唔到 避乜撚野狗"}]}